                "caption": "Figure 5:Met2Net effectively resolvesrepresentation inconsistencyby maintaining higher CKA values across layers compared to TAU. The TAU model exhibits a gradual increase in CKA values through the Translator section but maintains relatively lower CKA values overall. In contrast, Met2Net sustains higher CKA values across all layers, particularly in the Encoder and Translator sections, indicating improved representation consistency.",
